Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&\blur3}宇宙:太空边缘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着轰的一声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诞生了无限膨胀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在 所见超乎我们的想象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越了我们生存的限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}beyond the limits of our existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个空间我们称之为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a place we call "The Universe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想象有个地方 卫星90分钟可以绕地球一圈{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Imagine a place where a satellite can circle the earth in 90 minutes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}度假的游客一觉醒来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where a tourist on vacation wakes up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从太空酒店的房间里眺望出去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and takes in their view from a hotel room in space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或者一片涂层成为了致命武器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or where a speck of paint becomes a lethal weapon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会在航天飞机的侧面击出一个窟窿{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}able to blow a hole in the side of a spacecraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就是环地轨道上的现实{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These are the realities of Earth orbit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}通向太阳系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the gateway to the solar system...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是宇航员的地盘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and it's the turf of astronauts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太空垃圾{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}space junk...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}终极寻求刺激者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the ultimate thrill seeker.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和我们一起前往《太空边缘》{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Journey out with us to "The Edge of Space."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在不久的将来 人类将登上火箭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the not so distant future, a human will board a rocket...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐在开放的平台上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}sit on an open platform...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}升空120英里 直接进入环地轨道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and launch 120 miles straight up into Earth orbit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿上高科技的宇航服{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Dressed in a high-tech spacesuit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他目光透过石英涂层的头盔{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}he'll peer through a quartz-coated visor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一览无余 尽收眼底{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and take in an unparalleled view.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}近地轨道上 景色壮观{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Being in low Earth orbit is spectacular.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你举目眺望{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When you look up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到漆黑的外太空和群星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you see the inky blackness of outer space and the stars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星星甚至在白昼都在闪烁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the stars shining even in daytime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}低头俯视 你看到朦胧的蔚蓝色浩瀚大海{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Looking down, you see the hazy blue glow of this gigantic ocean...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就在你的脚下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}right underneath your feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这位观众是一位太空跳伞员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This observer is a space diver...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}新一代终极刺激迷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a new breed of ultimate thrill junkie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他解开安全带{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And as he unhooks from his safety harness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}站在太空边缘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and stands at the edge of space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看宇宙最后一眼{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}he takes one last look out to the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}纵身一跃 飞向地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and leaps, speeding towards Earth below.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太空跳跃许多未来的想法之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Space diving is one of many futuristic ideas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安排在环地轨道上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}planned for Earth orbit...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地球外围的太空区域{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the zone of space that surrounds Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}起点在海平面120英里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and begins 120 miles above sea level.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里是卫星及空间站的基地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's the home to satellites and the space station...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有 如果轨道旅行用品公司有自己之道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and, if Orbital Outfitters have their way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将是终极极限运动 太空跳伞的基地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the ultimate extreme sport: skydiving from space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}环地轨道是通往宇宙的门户{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Earth orbit is a window to the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许会成为地球本身的拓展{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and perhaps will become an extension of Earth itself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开展产业 探险 娱乐{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for industry, exploration, and fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是环地轨道上的环境完全不同于家园{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But the environment in Earth orbit is very different from home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里缺少氧气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oxygen ceases to exist here...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大气层{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the atmosphere...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个护卫地球的保护罩已不复存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that provides a protective shield around Earth disappears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙威胁窥视着勇敢的探险者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Cosmic threats lurk for those who dare explore here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们忽视了外太空是险地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We forget that outer space is dangerous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们忽视了在外太空 我们会碰上宇宙辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We forget that in outer space we have cosmic radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们会碰上太阳耀斑 碰上流星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we have solar flares, we have meteors...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会碰上太空垃圾{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we have space debris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是外太空里的障碍赛场{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's an obstacle course being out there in outer space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宛如自由落体跳伞运动迷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Like free-fall skydiving junkies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跳出飞机 飞向地面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}who leap out of planes and speed towards Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太空跳跃可能貌似终极刺激{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}space diving might seem like the ultimate thrill...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是其想法基于非常危险的意图{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but its idea is based on very serious intentions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乔纳森.克拉克博士 海军飞行医师{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Dr. Jonathan Clark, a Navy flight surgeon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}前海军高空跳伞员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and former Navy high altitude parachutist...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是太空跳跃概念的推手{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is one person behind the space diver concept...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是也有其强烈的个人原因{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but for very personal reasons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我被分配到航天局太空部门工作时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I was assigned to NASA to work on space operations...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的太太是个宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then my wife was an astronaut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哥伦比亚号 休斯顿 超高频通信设备检查{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Columbia, Houston, UHF comm check.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她牺牲于2003年的哥伦比亚号任务{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}She died on the Columbia mission in 2003.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然军事飞行员经常 会从陷于危险的飞机中安全弹出{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}While military pilots routinely eject safely from imperiled aircraft...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是目前尚没有疏散程序让宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}currently there is no evacuation procedure for astronauts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在灾难性事故中从航天器里弹出{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to eject from a spacecraft during a catastrophic event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约1%的机会{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}About one percent of the time...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们会遇上主助推火箭的失败{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we have a major booster rocket failure...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或者外太空的灾难{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or a catastrophe in outer space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许跳伞太空服会成为新的安全装备{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Perhaps the skydiver spacesuit will become a new safety device...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让宇航员用于飞行任务{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for astronauts to use on missions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其首次测试是16万英尺跳伞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and its first test is a 160,000-footjump.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了安全返回{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To survive reentry...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跳伞太空服有许多关键的特点:{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the skydiver spacesuit has many critical features:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}保护性连衣跳伞服绝缘了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a protective one-piece jumpsuit that insulates...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从零下40华氏度的太空环境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from the negative-40-degree Fahrenheit space environment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到464度的返回高温{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to the 464-degree heat generated from reentry...{\r}
