Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.95,0:43:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许未来50年里 在太空里...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's probably one of the most promising avenues to pursue...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.38,0:43:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最有希望追求的途径之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the next 50 years in space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是找到办法制造出廉价的太阳能收集器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is to find a way to make cheap solar collectors...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.35,0:43:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后在地面上建造收集天线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then build the collecting antennas on the ground...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样我们就可以使用取之不竭的太阳能{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so that we can use inexhaustible solar power...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.96,0:43:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来减少我们对我们地球上的有限供应的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to reduce our reliance on the finite supplies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.38,0:43:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}燃料和能源的依赖{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of fuel and energy we have here on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.00,0:43:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一点是肯定的:{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One thing is certain:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.75,0:43:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太空边缘是未来探索的切入口{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the edge of space is the entryway to future exploration...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.77,0:43:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是前往整个宇宙的停靠站{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a stopping point to the destinations across the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.59,0:43:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我非常激动 今后几十年里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm very excited about a future decades from now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.81,0:43:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}地球真的会是人类的伊甸园{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where the Earth really is the Garden of Eden of humanity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.91,0:43:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们会打理好我们的星球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where we've taken care of our planet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.38,0:43:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们的公园 我们的享受{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}our parks, our enjoyment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.47,0:44:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们关爱地球要做的就是照顾好它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the things that we love about the Earth are taken care of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.41,0:44:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们在制造方面所做的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And all the things that we do in terms of manufacturing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.76,0:44:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}资源的开采 能源 采集{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and resource extraction and energy and mining...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.81,0:44:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些通通都在太空中进行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}those things take place in space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.25,0:44:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然 近地轨道一路到整个太阳系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And, of course, low Earth orbit...is the gateway to the rest of the solar system.{\r}
